    "attributes": {
        "action": "Stop advanced and budgeting repayments on universal credit until Covid-19 goes",
        "additional_details": "My partner works self employed and at the current situation hasn't been affected by covid-19, yes we get a element of universal credit every month but, so we also pay off advanced and budgeting loans \u00a3100 plus a month, at the present time I believe the payments should be put on hold and the families get that, so they got enough to get by SURVIVE ,food,gas,electric,fuel for transport for work, extra food activity things  as children are home, I bet families already feeling the pinch",
        "background": "Stop all repayments on advanced payment and budgeting loans on universal credit until covid-19 is under control, giving families in hardship \u00a3100plus per month extra",
